Class Summary 
Class Description
Controller
Controller class that handles exceptions, creates appropriate Student objects, creates a StudentList adds / removes Students from the Student List.
Instate
InState Student Is a Student with the additional stipulation that they can have funds applied to their tuition if they are full time.
International
International Student Is a Student with the additional stipulation that they are not charged per credit and only charged the university fee and the international student fee if they are an exchange student.
Main  
Outstate
Outstate Student Is a Student with the addtional stipulation that they can have a discount per credit if they are from the tri-state area.
Prog2
Prog2 class intended to run the Program 2 Assignment.
Student
Student class that implements the Comparable interface.
StudentList
Contains methods to create an array of Students.
TuitionManager
TuitionManager class that handles exeptions, creates appropriate Student objects, creates a StudentList, and adds / removes Students from the Student List.
